properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Manasquan Inlet to Little Egg Inlet NJ out 20 nm; Coastal waters from Sandy Hook to Manasquan Inlet NJ out 20 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 18 at 3:16AM EST until February 18 at 9:00PM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southeast winds around 10-15kts with gusts up to 25 kts
and seas 4 to 5 feet expected.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Sandy Hook to Manasquan Inlet NJ
out 20 nm and Coastal waters from Manasquan Inlet to Little
Egg Inlet NJ out 20 nm.

* WHEN...Until 9 PM EST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 PM EST THIS EVENING
